    @Component
public class WindDataImpl
extends Object
implements WindDataAPI
    Return data over REST from time series for PredixNodejsStarter To turn on a 2nd time series: 1. uncomment the 3 sections below 2. in SecondaryTimeseriesConfig uncomment the @Component 3. in src/main/resources/application-cloud.properties uncomment the props for Option 1 or 2 4. in manifest.yml uncomment and fill in the properties for Option 1 or 2
